     flow — same lifecycle gap as Klaviyo/LoyaltyLion above. Pre-loading
     position:fixed in our <head> CSS wins the race because custom-theme.css
     and css-overrides.liquid parse before any app script downloads.

     Banner is bottom-aligned on desktop and mobile:
